<p><i><b>Anamnesis</b></i> (<a href="/wiki/Ancient_Greek_language" title="Ancient Greek language" class="mw-redirect">Ancient Greek</a>: <span lang="grc" xml:lang="grc">ἀνάμνησις</span> = "recollection, reminiscence" (literally "loss of forgetfulness") is a term used in <a href="/wiki/Medicine" title="Medicine">medicine</a>, <a href="/wiki/Philosophy" title="Philosophy">philosophy</a>, <a href="/wiki/Psychoanalysis" title="Psychoanalysis">psychoanalysis</a> and <a href="/wiki/Religion" title="Religion">religion</a>.</p>
